        <updateDate>2018-04-06T18:26:24Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Planes Ensuring Total Safety Act or the PETS Act </b></p> <p>This bill directs the Federal Aviation Administration to promulgate regulations: (1) prohibiting the storage of a live animal in an overhead compartment of a flight in air transportation, and (2) establishing fines for a violation of such prohibition.<br /></p>]]></text>
      </summary>
